title: Letterhead, "Kaywoodie Pipes, Inc."
inscribed: Printed in brown ink, upper left: Kaywoodie Pipes, Inc. Printed in black ink, upper center right: - World's Finest Pipes since 185/18 East 54th St. - New York 22, N.Y. - Phone Plaza 1 - 0770; upper right: Cable Address : Frankoris, N.Y.
